data.meta_description: Stanislaw Kostka Zamoyski with his wife, Zofia (née Czartoryska),and their family. 1884.muzeumzamoyskich.historia.org.pl Sebastian Ludwik Wilhelm Norblin (1796-1884)Princess Zofia Czartoryska(15 Sept. 1778-27 Feb31837)Polish noblewoman. She was the youngest daughter of Countess Izabela Czartoryska née Fleming and her husband Prince Adam Kazimierz Czartoryski,though her father may actually have been Count Franciszek Ksawery Branicki.She married Stanisław Kostka Zamoyski on 20 May 1798, at Puławy.
